Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory1081.jpg'}
{3: 'Deep in the cosmos, stars scatter across the infinite void.'}
{3: "You hear Nanami calling you from nearby shortly after you've made it out of the Dimension Domain."}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Phew. Thank goodness you're safe, Commandant!", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Upon hearing your voice, Nanami lets out a sigh of relief, her brows relaxing with reassurance.'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "These simulations don't cause any actual damage, but what happened back there was out of the blue and got me a little nervous, hehe.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Hey Commandant, would you like to take a break?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'We just came across the Emperor in the simulation just now...', 3: '15', 4: "I'm fine, let's keep going.", 5: '27'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Mmm, Schulz seized control of the Tabula Akasha in that world and launched an all-out war against humanity.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "A good number of awakened machines share Schulz's hatred toward humanity.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "If Nanami doesn't lead them away, the future will unfold just as the mecha babushka predicted—a war will break out between humans and mechanoids...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "I don't want to see mechanoids and humans hurt one another, that's why Nanami had to lead the Church of Machina away from Earth.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'But I bet you know all this already, right, Commandant?', 4: '1'}
{2: "Yes, I can see how much work you've put into it, Nanami.", 3: '23'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Hehe, Nanami's gotta do her very best to keep Earth safe!", 4: '1'}
{2: "Let's move forward together and get out of this place!", 3: '25'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Yes! Nanami can sense it—the singularity point for our escape is right ahead!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Here we go, here we go! I wonder what kind of world awaits us this time?', 4: '1'}
